    "en": {
      "title": "A girl fell into the bath and died",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Gampaha police say that an 18-year-old girl died after falling into a swimming pool in a house in Udugampola area.",
        "The police say that she was taken to the Gampaha District General Hospital when she fell into the swimming pool at home and by then she was already dead.",
        "Gampaha Acting Magistrate Nimal Ranasinghe conducted an on-site investigation regarding this incident this evening.",
        "He ordered the Gampaha Coroner to conduct the post-mortem and report the cause of death to the court."
      ],
